      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont get the goblin thing at all. can u just tell me what the signs of nitrogen deficiency are specifically? and like, if i use the sulfur to fix the ph, is there anything else i should watch out for so the plants dont die?",
      "source": "evaluator"
